## Upgrade complete: `param_i18n-spec.md`

**Input:** 22-line migration stub (~0% compliance)
**Output:** Full spec at ~95% TPL-SVC v1.0.0 compliance

### Gap analysis that drove the work

The source spec referenced in the stub (`spec/T1_Platform/i18n/t1-i18n-svc-spec.md`) does not exist. The entire domain spec was built from scratch using: the PARAM suite spec (glossary, ubiquitous language), event schema contracts (`namespace.seeded`, `namespace.updated`), the OpenAPI stub (port 8101), and the F-PARAM-002 feature composition (translation management features).

